        </div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Google Business Profile</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">Daily posts. Reviews answered in minutes. <span class="accent">Q&A live.</span></h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">theStacc posts to GBP every day in your brand voice, replies to reviews within minutes, and answers Google Q&A before competitors notice. Multi-location ready up to 500 locations.</p>
        <ul class="bento-list">
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Daily GBP posts · offers, updates, events</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Review replies in &lt; 5 minutes</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Q&A monitored · brand-trained answers</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bento-cta">See GBP integration <span class="arrow">→</span></div>
      </a>

      <a class="bento-card" href="#rank-tracking">
        <div class="bento-num">02</div>
        <div class="bento-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Map Pack rank tracking</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">A 5×5 geo-grid · <span class="accent">your rank from every corner.</span></h4>
